import React from 'react'
import Timeline from '@mui/lab/Timeline';
import TimelineItem from '@mui/lab/TimelineItem';
import TimelineSeparator from '@mui/lab/TimelineSeparator';
import TimelineConnector from '@mui/lab/TimelineConnector';
import TimelineContent from '@mui/lab/TimelineContent';
import TimelineDot from '@mui/lab/TimelineDot';
import TimelineOppositeContent from '@mui/lab/TimelineOppositeContent';
import { createTheme, ThemeProvider, Typography } from '@mui/material';
const theme = createTheme({
  typography: {
      fontFamily: [
          'Poppins',
          'sans-serif'
      ].join(','),
  }
});

theme.typography.h5 = {
    fontSize: '1em',
    [theme.breakpoints.up('lg')]: {
        fontSize: '1em',
    },
    [theme.breakpoints.down('lg')]: {
        fontSize: '1em',
    },
    [theme.breakpoints.down('md')]: {
        fontSize: '0.875em',
    },
    [theme.breakpoints.down('sm')]: {
        fontSize: '0.75em',
    },
    [theme.breakpoints.down('xs')]: {
        fontSize: '0.6em',
    },
};

const MyTimeline = () => {
  return (
    <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
    
    <Timeline position="alternate">
      <TimelineItem>
        <TimelineOppositeContent>
          09:30 am
        </TimelineOppositeContent>
        <TimelineSeparator>
          <TimelineDot />
          <TimelineConnector  />
        </TimelineSeparator>
        <TimelineContent variant="h5">4th Century BC, Greece
        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div" align="center">
                          "The first description of bodies falling downwards towards the centre was related to their nature was documented by the Greek philosopher Aristotle. This nature of objects getting attracted was due to their gravitas or heaviness."
                        </Typography>
        </TimelineContent>
      </TimelineItem>
      <TimelineItem>
        <TimelineOppositeContent>
          10:00 am
        </TimelineOppositeContent>
        <TimelineSeparator>
          <TimelineDot />
          <TimelineConnector />
        </TimelineSeparator>
        <TimelineContent variant="h5">Code</TimelineContent>
      </TimelineItem>
      <TimelineItem>
        <TimelineOppositeContent>
          12:00 am
        </TimelineOppositeContent>
        <TimelineSeparator>
          <TimelineDot />
          <TimelineConnector />
        </TimelineSeparator>
        <TimelineContent variant="h5">Sleep</TimelineContent>
      </TimelineItem>
      <TimelineItem>
        <TimelineOppositeContent>
          9:00 am
        </TimelineOppositeContent>
        <TimelineSeparator>
          <TimelineDot/>
          <TimelineConnector />
        </TimelineSeparator>
        <TimelineContent variant="h5">Repeat</TimelineContent>
      </TimelineItem>
      <TimelineItem>
        <TimelineOppositeContent>
          09:30 am
        </TimelineOppositeContent>
        <TimelineSeparator>
          <TimelineDot />
          <TimelineConnector  />
        </TimelineSeparator>
        <TimelineContent variant="h5">Eat</TimelineContent>
      </TimelineItem>
      <TimelineItem>
        <TimelineOppositeContent>
          10:00 am
        </TimelineOppositeContent>
        <TimelineSeparator>
          <TimelineDot />
          <TimelineConnector />
        </TimelineSeparator>
        <TimelineContent variant="h5">Code</TimelineContent>
      </TimelineItem>
      <TimelineItem>
        <TimelineOppositeContent>
          12:00 am
        </TimelineOppositeContent>
        <TimelineSeparator>
          <TimelineDot />
          <TimelineConnector />
        </TimelineSeparator>
        <TimelineContent variant="h5">Sleep</TimelineContent>
      </TimelineItem>
      <TimelineItem>
        <TimelineOppositeContent>
          9:00 am
        </TimelineOppositeContent>
        <TimelineSeparator>
          <TimelineDot/>
          <TimelineConnector />
        </TimelineSeparator>
        <TimelineContent variant="h5">Repeat</TimelineContent>
      </TimelineItem>
    </Timeline>
    </ThemeProvider>
  )
}

export default MyTimeline
